      "**The simmer pot.** For a warm, all-natural lift, simmer a small pot of water with **citrus slices, a cinnamon stick, and a few sprigs of rosemary or thyme** for twenty minutes. It gently scents the whole room and is lovely before guests arrive — just never leave it unattended or let it boil dry.",
